## Template Usage Notes

This template is used by `scripts/generate-community-report.sh` to create community/developer update reports.

### Narrative Sections

Sections marked with `<!-- AI_NARRATIVE_START: section_name -->` are placeholders for human or AI-generated narrative content focused on community engagement and developer experience.

### Cadence

This template supports both monthly and bi-weekly cadences:

```bash
# Monthly (default)
./scripts/generate-community-report.sh

# Bi-weekly
./scripts/generate-community-report.sh --biweekly

# Dry run
./scripts/generate-community-report.sh --dry-run
```
